{"tid":780673,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[食飯慎入]大家有冇試過嚿屎黐住啲毛跌唔到落去","createTime":"2018-08-15T10:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T12:48:35.000Z","uid":176311,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b6ba38c09ce336f0cd8348fee0f75808285327","tid":780673,"uid":176311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今朝我屙屎。當我諗住享受咇屎出嚟嘅快感嘅時候，我feel到嚿屎擺脫咗地心吸力嘅束縛，黐咗喺肛門啲毛嗰度。我諗住chok嚿屎落去啦，點知好似粒睾丸咁，fing嚟fing去，都係跌唔到落去。我就忍無可忍，諗住抆翻嚿屎出嚟，點知原來唔係咁易㗎。抆咗好多轉，重係有一pat屎黐實咗啲毛。最後，我決定放棄我隻右手。我衝入浴室，左手攞個花灑省我個屎眼，右手就喺度撩個窿，整乾淨啲毛，嗰種感覺真係極度嘔心。最慘嘅係，嗰浸屎味一直揮之不去。結果，由屙屎到抆屎，用咗足足半個鐘。我洗咗十幾次手，啲屎味到依家都重喺度呀屌！！"},{"pid":"701c7b87ccb9337befc1e2e005065fd236455294","tid":780673,"uid":176311,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"隻手重臭過毒撚浸味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbfafb8621e382c0c9db47c22c793de0cf80d37","tid":780673,"uid":176311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T10:23:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a5570a29b1b1efac9e6a1612f68aa30d59d349a","tid":780673,"uid":176311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T10:26:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6fc14ad1e745adaa0d7575db71c7ddcfd3a15aa","tid":780673,"uid":176311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T10:30:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9591b0eb102b6452ecfdb5de5c8812244ebca370","tid":780673,"uid":40938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T10:31:43.000Z","msg":"見你咁慘，冇人應你，幫你推下"},{"pid":"c4f47fb9275675717cb4f629f39d7e773cb72437","tid":780673,"uid":176311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9591b0eb102b6452ecfdb5de5c8812244ebca370","tid":780673,"uid":40938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T10:31:43.000Z","msg":"見你咁慘，冇人應你，幫你推下"},"citedBy":